name: Lugano dresser, carved fronts
description: Looking sleek, elegant and exclusive, Lugano will solve all your storage needs without breaking a sweat. Though utterly practical, you will not find this chest of drawers lacking in beauty. A stunning finish and an elegant look make this modern chest of drawers fit in anywhere. The design is completed with bevelled edges. This fine detail ensures harmony and brings an elegance and exclusivity to the expression. Leg options and soft close mechanism included.
